───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

IDEA #21: "Manufacturing and Engineering - Find Technical Talent Fast"

Sector Focus: Manufacturing, automotive, capital equipment companies
Core Problem: Manufacturing companies use old-school hiring; struggle to find engineers
Positioning Message: "Bring modern hiring to traditional manufacturing"
Key Value Proposition: Find qualified engineers faster than traditional methods
Target Audience: Manufacturing HR teams, factory-based companies
Metric Focus: Engineer quality improvement, hiring speed
Content Angle: Manufacturing sector transformation stories, old vs new hiring comparison
Why It Works: Massive opportunity; manufacturing hiring is antiquated

Implementation Examples:
