SECTION 7: CONTENT PILLARS FOR ORGANIC GROWTH

For each positioning idea, create six pieces of content:

CONTENT TYPE 1: BEFORE & AFTER STORIES (ROI Focus)
Frequency: 2-3 per week
Formats: LinkedIn posts, blog articles, case study PDFs
Messaging: "Our clients went from X to Y in Z time"
Example: "From 60-day hiring cycle to 21 days: Startup's transformation story"

CONTENT TYPE 2: RECRUITER CONFESSIONS (Pain Point Validation)
Frequency: Weekly
Formats: LinkedIn carousel posts, blog stories, video testimonials
Messaging: "Every recruiter struggles with X - here's how we solved it"
Example: "The resume fraud that cost us ₹20 lakhs - and how we prevented it"

CONTENT TYPE 3: INDUSTRY TREND REPORTS (Authority Building)
Frequency: Quarterly
Formats: Data-rich infographics, downloadable reports, webinars
Messaging: "What 10,000 hiring teams are doing"
Example: "Q4 2024 India Hiring Trends Report"

CONTENT TYPE 4: COMPETITOR COMPARISON (Convincing Content)
Frequency: Monthly
Formats: Blog comparisons, webinar deep-dives
Messaging: "Why traditional hiring costs you more"
Example: "Manual hiring vs. automated assessment: Cost and quality comparison"

CONTENT TYPE 5: FOUNDER/LEADER INTERVIEWS (Inspiration & Proof)
Frequency: Bi-weekly
Formats: Video interviews, podcast series, blog features
Messaging: "How [Founder] hires 100 people per month"
Example: "Podcast: How Swiggy scaled hiring with smart assessment"

CONTENT TYPE 6: RECRUITER ACHIEVEMENT CELEBRATIONS (Community Building)
Frequency: Weekly
Formats: Short video testimonials, LinkedIn LIVE sessions
Messaging: "Celebrate recruiter wins"
Example: "Meet the recruiter who placed 50 quality hires in one month"

